                "Lanzhou (RIBLL)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 36Ar primary beam was accelerated by HIRFL, the",
                "beam energy was 69 MeV/u. The radioactive ion beam",
                "was produced by bombarding the primary target Ni(92.3",
                "mg/cm2)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The secondary target was 12C (109.7 mg/cm2)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two plastic scintillation detectors were used",
                "to measure the time of flight (TOF)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " DE detector was a Au-Si surface barrier",
                "semiconductor detector before the target. After the",
                "target, there were 5 Au-Si surface barrier",
                "semiconductor detectors, the thickness of 5 detectors",
                "were 150, 150, 700, 700 and 2000 um, the resolution",
                "less than 1.8%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "EDE",
                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The particles were identified by the",
                "TOF and dE before target. After target, the outgoing",
                "particles were identified by the dE-E method."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Statistical uncertainty."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The beam energies of 17F, 18F, 19F, 20F and 21F at",
                "the centre of the 12C target are ranged from 16 to 33",
                "MeV/u. The measured cross sections were transformed",
                "into the values at 30 MeV/u by Shen's",
                "parameterization. The change due to this",
                "transformation is within 5%."
              ]
            }
          ],
